The first glimmers of hope are starting to emerge for Elon and his
$44 billion deal for X, which was once derided as one of the worst acquisit=
ions since the financial crisis. With the debt now trading at or near par (=
!!), here=E2=80=99s a deconstruction of an entirely improbable turnaround.

William D. Cohan ( https://puck.news/author/william-cohan/?utm_campaign=3DD=
ry+Powder+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%282%2F16%2F25%29&utm_content=3DDry+Powder+-+SUBSCR=
IBERS+%282%2F16%2F25%29&utm_medium=3Demail_action&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io&=
utm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a )
William D. Cohan ( https://puck.news/author/william-cohan/?utm_campaign=3DD=
ry+Powder+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%282%2F16%2F25%29&utm_content=3DDry+Powder+-+SUBSCR=
